------------------------------------------------------------
   20/12 95. Henry Michael Lassen

* Added to graphicsadds:

    - drawIconResource: An operation to draw an iconresource.

* Added to guienvadds:

    - bringBack: A windowitem is send behind all siblings
    
    - launchFile: File is executed.

    - setWindowIcon: Allows the icon for a specific window to be
                     changed.

    - setApplIcon: Allows the icon of the application to be changed.

* Added fragmentgroups (with body files):

   - navigationkeys: Contains navigation keys constants LeftArrow,
                     RightArrow, UpArrow, DownArrow.
 
   - rasteradds: Containts the patterns:
                 
                 iconResource: bitMap (# ... #);
                 bitmapResource: bitMap (# ... #);

* Changed tableviewbody to use the navigationkeys.

------------------------------------------------------------
   6/2 96. Henry Michael Lassen

* The library raster_xpmfile supports reading Xpm files, by
  adding the following operation to bitmap:

     readFromXPMfile:
       (* Reads the contents of the XPMfile into THIS(bitmap) *)
       (# filename: ^text;
       enter filename[]
       do ...
       #);

  To use this library you must set the environment variable
  LD_LIBRARY_PATH as follows:

  setenv LD_LIBRARY_PATH /users/beta/X11/Xpm/lib

------------------------------------------------------------

   25/5 2001. Karsten Strandgaard Jorgensen

* Error corrected in private/winnt/textfieldadds_ntibody.bet
  Added a call of update at the end of enableUpdate

------------------------------------------------------------

  11/7 2001. Mads Brogger Enevoldsen

M textfieldadds.bet
M private/X11/textfieldadds_X11body.bet
M private/winnt/textfieldadds_ntibody.bet

* In textfieldadds added a new pattern updateLine, 
  to make it possible to update a single line after a 
  disableUpdate. 
  Implemented on Unix and Windows.


------------------------------------------------------------

  17/7 2001 Mads Brogger Enevoldsen

M textfieldadds.bet
M private/X11/textfieldadds_X11body.bet
M private/winnt/textfieldadds_ntibody.bet

* Added a new pattern updateRegion, which takes two
  parameters (y1,y2) and updates the rectangle (0,y1)
  (size.xMax,y2)

